UDI Static Properties Implementation

On non-ELF generating OSes, you need to implement your own
get_abi_sprops/set_abi_sprops. If your OS at least allows
you to add extra sections to a object file, you should be
able to do something like I've done here in order to
generate an appropriate udiprops section.

--Steven Bytnar <sbytnar@users.sourceforge.net>

